{"tid":844954,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"(暈到仆街)良性陣發性位置性眩暈","createTime":"2018-10-02T09:37:39.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-02T17:53:51.000Z","uid":86008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"1c2cb0019537c1c2421dbf78cdee705035a88bfc","tid":844954,"uid":86008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:37:39.000Z","msg":"有無巴絲都會有咁嘅情況呢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;良性陣發性位置性眩暈（簡稱 BPPV）是最常見<br />\r\n的一種眩暈。突然改變體位姿勢通常會造成眩<br />\r\n暈。 當人的內耳平衡器官（內耳石）受到干擾時，BPPV 就會出現。內耳石是體積微小的晶體狀器官，一旦脫位，便會導致眩暈症狀出現。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n通常頭突然間郁得大方向<br />\n就會天旋地轉咁暈10幾秒<br />\n我係訓覺個陣一轉左訓就暈到仆街 眼球震動<br />\n7月第一次出現過 今日又出現過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n依家個人暈下暈下咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 一暈就想嘔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n食藥都無咩用 都要等幾日先慢慢變好<br />\n睇下有無同路人都有咁嘅情況 取下暖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"689eafc5624dab0084aa0dd0208e2a6fa6d95db8","tid":844954,"uid":177089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:46:09.000Z","msg":"無"},{"pid":"80edebf59d2f5a5afe6e7e7dc9cfad2bd87776e8","tid":844954,"uid":208270,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:47:03.000Z","msg":"痞低起身見頭暈"},{"pid":"055f161e27af370a6ad5548ccae87971b0220043","tid":844954,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"同耳水不平衡有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3d70f651654e6b0216149130de6cfe13ff5595f9","tid":844954,"uid":86008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"055f161e27af370a6ad5548ccae87971b0220043","tid":844954,"uid":91633,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T09:52:25.000Z","msg":"同耳水不平衡有咩分別？<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T10:18:08.000Z","msg":"耳水不平衡係連耳仔都有事 例如係耳鳴<br />\n而且係會暈好耐<br />\n相反位置性頭暈係唔會影響聽覺 好快暈完<br />\n暈係因為頭郁動嘅位置<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"810470f33600dce95f59b5eb798601de2a1ae471","tid":844954,"uid":15139,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T13:28:52.000Z","msg":"可以去睇物理治療"},{"pid":"dbd49e9c15ddfbfd99dcd8bee640460d6fdc86e7","tid":844954,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"巴打試下自己做個復位睇下有無改善<br />\n小心每次轉頭同坐起身會暈到仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9SLm76jQg3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9SLm76jQg3g&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e81ea608\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9SLm76jQg3g</a>"},{"pid":"3c82e135c585415ac54500aa57b6e31365c70b13","tid":844954,"uid":45161,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:20:34.000Z","msg":"試過，醫生話耳水不平衡<br />\n但隻耳係冇問題<br />\n話冇得根治"},{"pid":"8310910e72da67757a2eeb87d126e6bd9f1c34c8","tid":844954,"uid":59671,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:23:02.000Z","msg":"我連續三晚一瞓低就暈<br />\n起身又冇事㗎喎<br />\n有兩三次轉身暈到個人好似失去咗意識幾秒咁<br />\n好辛苦"},{"pid":"1af5a6ed6a71b9c67629cdab7c0b53e7b9c4a78b","tid":844954,"uid":92804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"dbd49e9c15ddfbfd99dcd8bee640460d6fdc86e7","tid":844954,"uid":95519,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:17:54.000Z","msg":"巴打試下自己做個復位睇下有無改善<br />\n小心每次轉頭同坐起身會暈到仆街<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/9SLm76jQg3g\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2F9SLm76jQg3g&d=kQFAM6terdWJr1P%2FpqNKgP%2F4Bxi6eTjWtF%2F0WJNXpvw%3D&h=e81ea608\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/9SLm76jQg3g</a>"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-02T17:53:51.000Z","msg":"可以試做 <br />\n但係粒耳石跌落唔同嘅位會有唔同癥況<br />\n做錯咗方向反而更加暈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n建議搵番物理治療師查詢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}